Package: maxentcppCompTest
Type: Package
Title: Comparison Tests for maxentcpp and Maxent Outputs
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-04-10
Authors@R: c(
    person("alrobles", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "alrobles@example.com"))
Description: A testing package that compares the outputs of the C++ MaxEnt
    implementation (maxentcpp, from alrobles/Maxent R-package) against the
    original Java-based Maxent (via dismo). Uses a mock 10-by-10 raster
    example with predefined environmental layers and 10 occurrence records
    to validate that both implementations produce equivalent results.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: Java (>= 8)
Imports:
    stats,
    terra,
    utils
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    maxentcpp,
    dismo,
    raster,
    rJava
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Encoding: UTF-8
